# {{context|US|lang=en}} A [[footpath]], usually [[pave]]d, at the side of a [[road]] for the use of [[pedestrian]]s; a [[pavement]] {{qualifier|UK}} or footpath {{qualifier|Australia}}; by extension, any paved footpath, even if not located at the side of a road.

